cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Activation Geometry for Honesty Failures"
message: "If you use this artifact, please cite the repository."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Ghoshal
    given-names: Rajarshi
repository-code: "https://github.com/rajarshighoshal/geometry-of-deception"
abstract: >
  Public artifact record for activation-space experiments on honesty failures in language models.
  The release includes a paired synthetic-pressure pilot showing that pressure-induced caving to
  false premises is strongly decodable from Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct residual-stream activations,
  plus a graded PASS/FAIL control audit showing that an apparent steering win fails under
  bidirectional error-type auditing.
license: MIT
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-06-24"
